  "_comment_scope": "Bundle 3 of 6 for Laura Jennings. Da Vinci PAS (Prior Authorization Support) IG. This bundle represents the $submit operation payload sent from Harrodsburg Family Dentistry to Anthem BCBS Kentucky requesting prior authorization for D3330, D2740, and D2393. In a live PAS implementation this would be POSTed to: POST [base]/Claim/$submit. References clinical documentation from Bundle 2 (DTR). PAS IG: http://hl7.org/fhir/us/davinci-pas",

  "_comment_pas_operation": "Production deployment note: The $submit operation wraps this Bundle. The Claim resource with use='preauthorization' is the focal resource. The payer returns a ClaimResponse synchronously or asynchronously (see Bundle 4). Dental-specific note: PAS for dental was tested at the January 2026 HL7 Connectathon. CRD (Coverage Requirements Discovery via CDS Hooks) and DTR (Documentation Templates and Rules) are architecturally upstream of this submission but are not yet implemented in dental PMS systems as of mid-2026.",

